# AI Portfolio Backend

Production-style FastAPI backend powering Lahari M’s engineering portfolio.

This backend handles:

- AI chatbot inference
- portfolio analytics
- recruiter interaction tracking
- visitor sessions
- operational APIs
- admin analytics dashboard

Built to demonstrate:
- backend engineering
- async architecture thinking
- AI infrastructure integration
- production deployment workflows

---

# Architecture

Frontend Portfolio
→ Analytics Tracking
→ FastAPI Backend
→ Groq LLM API
→ SQLite Analytics DB

---

# Features

## AI Portfolio Assistant

LLM-powered assistant capable of answering questions about:

- projects
- backend systems
- async workflows
- engineering decisions
- experience
- achievements

Powered by:
- Groq API
- Llama 3.3 70B
- custom portfolio context injection

---

## Visitor Analytics

Tracks:

- total visits
- session activity
- time spent
- page visits
- recruiter interaction flow

---

## Hidden Admin Dashboard

Server-rendered operational dashboard:

/admin

Displays:

- total visitors
- average session duration
- most visited pages
- recent activity

---

# Tech Stack

## Backend

- FastAPI
- Python
- SQLAlchemy
- SQLite

## AI

- Groq API
- Llama 3.3 70B

## Infrastructure

- Uvicorn
- CORS Middleware
- Environment Variables
- Production Deployment Ready

